I apologize for my mistake once again. After reviewing the code again, I realized that the problem lies in the definition of the probability thresholds for the different levels of confidence. The original definition I provided did not take into account the two-tailed nature of the normal distribution.

Here is a corrected version of the code that should work as expected:


```
scalaimport org.apache.commons.math3.distribution.NormalDistribution

